---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro'
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro'
---

<Base
  title="Biohub · Maximilian Lombardo"
  description="Full detail on Maximilian Lombardo's product work at Chan Zuckerberg Biohub: CELLxGENE, Foundation Models & Virtual Cells Platform, VariantFormer, Automated Annotation Engine, and strategic biosafety work."
>
  <div class="wrap">
    <a href="/" class="back">← Back to home</a>

    <header class="page-header">
      <span class="label">01 / WORK</span>
      <h1><a href="https://www.czbiohub.org/">Biohub</a> <span class="muted">/ CZI</span></h1>
      <p class="tagline">Product for AI research &amp; cell science</p>
      <span class="badge">CURRENT</span>
    </header>

    <div class="content">
      <p class="lead">
        At Biohub (formerly <a href="https://chanzuckerberg.com/">Chan Zuckerberg Initiative</a>), I work
        on product for AI research and cell science, collaborating with computational biologists, ML
        researchers, and engineers.
      </p>

      <div class="section">
        <h2>CELLxGENE</h2>
        <p>
          Partnered with product leadership to define vision for <a href="https://cellxgene.cziscience.com/">CELLxGENE</a>,
          translating scientific requirements into roadmaps and specifications. Led cross-functional teams
          to deliver the visualization, data discovery, and API tools for AI models, embeddings, and data
          access, validating features via prototyping, model evaluation, and UX research.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="section">
        <h2>Foundation Models &amp; Virtual Cells Platform</h2>
        <p>
          Delivered biological foundation models to our <a href="https://virtualcellmodels.cziscience.com/">Virtual Cells Platform</a>,
          evolving from external model curation to orchestrating internal releases that bridged AI Research,
          Engineering, and Product. For <a href="https://github.com/czi-ai/variantformer">VariantFormer</a>,
          leveraged Claude Code to engineer the technical GTM suite including interactive model playgrounds
          and Remotion videos.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="section">
        <h2>Automated Annotation Engine</h2>
        <p>
          Led 0-1 build of an automated annotation engine, delivering the model (VAE/Logistic Regression)
          and UI.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="section">
        <h2>Strategic Work</h2>
        <p>
          Developed strategic biosafety briefings that CZI leadership presented to the
          <a href="https://www.frontiermodelforum.org/">Frontier Model Forum</a>. Co-organized
          <a href="https://scverse.org/">scverse</a> (with NVIDIA, TileDB) and represented the
          organization at <a href="https://neurips.cc/">NeurIPS</a>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <Footer />
</Base>

<style>
  .wrap {
    max-width: 960px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 40px 40px 80px;
  }

  .back {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--t3);
    text-decoration: none;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
    transition: color 0.15s;
  }

  .back:hover {
    color: var(--ww);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .page-header {
    margin-bottom: 52px;
    padding-bottom: 40px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
  }

  .label {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    color: var(--red);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: clamp(32px, 5vw, 56px);
    font-weight: 200;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    line-height: 1.05;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  h1 a {
    color: var(--ww);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  h1 a:hover {
    text-decoration: none;
    color: var(--ww);
  }

  .muted {
    color: var(--red);
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  .tagline {
    font-size: 16px;
    color: var(--t2);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .badge {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    color: var(--red);
    border: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--red) 40%, transparent);
    border-radius: 9999px;
    padding: 5px 10px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .lead {
    font-size: 17px;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--t2);
    max-width: 680px;
    margin-bottom: 52px;
  }

  .content {
    max-width: 680px;
  }

  .section {
    margin-bottom: 44px;
    padding-bottom: 44px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line-faint);
  }

  .section:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 300;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    color: var(--ww);
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }

  p {
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--t2);
  }

  a {
    color: var(--red);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .wrap {
      padding: 24px 20px 60px;
    }
  }
</style>
